### Authority Weighting

#### [NEW] [authority.py](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/authority.py)

Weighted formula per claim:
```
weighted = (w1 ├Ś recency) + (w2 ├Ś source_rank) + (w3 ├Ś citation_density)
         + (w4 ├Ś worker_confidence) + (w5 ├Ś cosine_similarity) + (w6 ├Ś coverage_score)
```
Default weights: `w1=0.15, w2=0.20, w3=0.15, w4=0.20, w5=0.15, w6=0.15`

