### Cross-Worker Agreement

#### [NEW] [consensus.py](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/consensus.py)

- Agreement score = `# workers supporting claim / total workers`
- Support detection: keyword overlap between claim and worker outputs

---

### Engine Orchestrator

#### [NEW] [engine.py](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/engine.py)

`AdjudicationEngine.adjudicate(synthesis_result, merged_claims, ...)`:

1. For each [ConflictCandidate](file:///c:/HelioX/synthesis/schemas.py#43-53):
   a. Run semantic contradiction detection
   b. Compute authority scores for both claims
   c. Compute agreement scores
   d. **Re-verification loop** (max 2 rounds): re-score if unresolved
   e. Apply resolution policy: winner = highest combined score; if still unresolved, reduce confidence
2. Build final selected evidence set (non-conflicting + winners)
3. Return `AdjudicationResult`

